22https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manned_Maneuvering_Unit\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMMU\u003C/a\u003E and an environment it worked in I\u0027m flying all the way!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:happy:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/happy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:happy:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-08-22T05:06:18Z\u0022 title=\u002208/22/2023 05:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Aug 22\u0022\u003EAugust 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by James Kerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eadded link\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}